ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectOrder Amending the CCRFTA Sugar Aggregate Quantity Limit Remission Order
PrecisORDER AMENDING THE CCRFTA SUGAR AGGREGATE QUANTITY LIMIT REMISSION ORDER to adjust the tariff items listed in the definition section of the CCRFTA Sugar Aggregate Quantity Limit Remission Order, which remits customs duties paid or payable on certain quantities of refined sugar originating in Costa Rica, with the coming into force of the CPFTA.
